snippet.title: Timothy vs the Aliens - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Timothy vs the Aliens is a platformer, adventure and action video game where you will play as a gangster named Timothy, who lives in a black & white period and fights against the full-colored aliens that have invaded his city.


Nintendo Switch - (pre-order 15/07, launch date 22/07)

Steam - (now available for Wishlist, launch date 22/07) https://store.steampowered.com/app/853060/Timothy_vs_the_Aliens/
